Kazunori UEDA (Waseda University)
The exciting time and hard-won lessons of the Fifth Generation
Computer Project

Atze Dijkstra (Utrecht University)
UHC: Coping with Compiler Complexity


TUTORIALS

Andreas Abel, on Agda
